{"id":91069461,"iid":14,"project_id":12955687,"title":"packages.yml refers to a deprecated version of dbt_utils","description":"## Context 

fishtown-analytics/* packages have been renamed dbt-labs/*

## Problem

Installing a package that depends on fishtown-analytics/dbt_utils creates duplicated package name error when using other packages that depend on dbt-labs/dbt_utils
This creates packages incompatibility and difficulties to upgrade to dbt's latest version

## Example

Upgrading to dbt 0.20.0 and installing these packages should create an error 

```
packages:
  - package: dbt-labs/dbt_utils
    version: 0.7.0
  - package: dbt-labs/audit_helper
    version: 0.4.0
  - git: https://gitlab.com/gitlab-data/snowflake_spend.git
    revision: v1.2.0
  - package: dbt-labs/dbt_external_tables
    version: 0.7.0
```","state":"opened","created_at":"2021-07-29T07:58:08.871Z","updated_at":"2022-05-02T20:24:23.772Z","closed_at":null,"closed_by":null,"labels":[],"milestone":null,"assignees":[],"author":{"id":6214107,"username":"loicchesneau","name":"Lo√Øc Chesneau","state":"active","avatar_url":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/74e4a0137b86a49a6cb8db473b0c47d4?s=80&d=identicon","web_url":"https://gitlab.com/loicchesneau"},"type":"ISSUE","assignee":null,"user_notes_count":5,"merge_requests_count":0,"upvotes":1,"downvotes":0,"due_date":null,"confidential":false,"discussion_locked":null,"issue_type":"issue","web_url":"https://gitlab.com/gitlab-data/snowflake_spend/-/issues/14","time_stats":{"time_estimate":0,"total_time_spent":0,"human_time_estimate":null,"human_total_time_spent":null},"task_completion_status":{"count":0,"completed_count":0},"weight":null,"blocking_issues_count":0,"has_tasks":false,"_links":{"self":"https://gitlab.com/api/v4/projects/12955687/issues/14","notes":"https://gitlab.com/api/v4/projects/12955687/issues/14/notes","award_emoji":"https://gitlab.com/api/v4/projects/12955687/issues/14/award_emoji","project":"https://gitlab.com/api/v4/projects/12955687","closed_as_duplicate_of":null},"references":{"short":"#14","relative":"#14","full":"gitlab-data/snowflake_spend#14"},"severity":"UNKNOWN","moved_to_id":null,"service_desk_reply_to":null,"epic_iid":null,"epic":null,"iteration":null,"health_status":null}

{"id":106802088,"iid":15,"project_id":12955687,"title":"Getting issues and warning upgrading the new dbt version 1.0.4","description":"## Context
Upgrade DBT version 1.0.4 

## Problem
using the package snowflake spend i anm getting errors and warnings based on the recomendations , this upgrade creates packages incompatibility and difficulties to upgrade to dbt's latest version

## Example
Upgrading to dbt 1.0.4 and installing these packages should create an error and warnings 

#Before
```
packages:
  - package: gitlabhq/snowflake_spend
    version: 1.2.0
  - package: fishtown-analytics/dbt_utils
    version: 0.6.4
```

#After option 1
```
packages:
  - package: dbt-labs/dbt_utils
    version: 0.8.4
  - package: gitlabhq/snowflake_spend
    version: 1.2.0
```

Result : error installing the package 
The `fishtown-analytics/dbt_utils` package is deprecated in favor of
`dbt-labs/dbt_utils`. Please update your `packages.yml` configuration to use
`dbt-labs/dbt_utils` instead.
18:41:15  Encountered an error:
Found duplicate project "dbt_utils". This occurs when a dependency has the same project name as some other dependency.


#Before option 2
https://gitlab.com/gitlab-data/snowflake_spend/-/issues/14

```
packages:
  - git: "https://github.com/fishtown-analytics/dbt-utils.git"
    revision: 0.7.6 # tag or branch name
  
  - git: https://gitlab.com/gitlab-data/snowflake_spend.git
    revision: 6f45b467c478df1c67d19cf6d4cbb8e05a710662
```

Result : a lot of warnings with the new dbt version
